{"tid":510727,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港啲口音同廣州口音最接近 但明明隔咗兩個市","createTime":"2017-12-26T17:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T19:08:54.000Z","uid":139766,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"86b8e3755352405ea31904bbddd79e63bc76bb5c","tid":510727,"uid":139766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"如果唔係香港人多懶音 我諗口音都係一樣<br />\n香港同廣州隔住深圳同東莞<br />\n深圳同東莞都有佢哋嘅口音<br />\n照計香港都係偏深圳口音<br />\n有無人知點解？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/27/013129_85520af217f900115c1a8926d08de430.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2F013129_85520af217f900115c1a8926d08de430.png&h=8ddaa9b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fde36b96c63dd70a0b3e5449f69682c5017efb69","tid":510727,"uid":126590,"like":15,"dislike":54,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"你都忽嘅！<br />\n因爲香港人全部都係由大陸移民落黎囉，唔通靠恥笑人地就真係割裂到個關係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050040307b5400b6aecfdb15f91d63800c4ce81d","tid":510727,"uid":56533,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:03:40.000Z","msg":"地理上遠, 但其實交通上近<br />\n<br />\n詳見: 九廣鐵路<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/03/Kowloon%E2%80%93Canton_Railway.jpg/800px-Kowloon%E2%80%93Canton_Railway.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F03%2FKowloon%25E2%2580%2593Canton_Railway.jpg%2F800px-Kowloon%25E2%2580%2593Canton_Railway.jpg&h=1bb6b48f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ffa5f8a3b4e4cc8e0fc2a66d9b7bcb528219b8d","tid":510727,"uid":36421,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T18:56:56.000Z","msg":"深圳有幾多係本地人先得嫁 好多識廣東話都未必係本地人啦 仲未計成堆外省既。 廣州以前都本身人多咪無咁易比人洗牌囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0cac76ea8a6238b98b63a9b32fadabf93717af","tid":510727,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:01:20.000Z","msg":"Wfc 完"},{"pid":"c513e85784d9bf3bc7fdbed77dae89f0afb2d48a","tid":510727,"uid":115197,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:54:33.000Z","msg":"以前得香港北上下一個大城市係廣州<br />\n東莞只係小城 深圳係條村<br />\n啲人係去都去廣州<br />\n所以口音咁近"},{"pid":"ea5f563d78c13e28fcf097a228873322313eff48","tid":510727,"uid":19072,"like":5,"dislike":45,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:57:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e67a2d1578eb293350d693e40cc37dca738cc88","tid":510727,"uid":57269,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T20:35:15.000Z","msg":"東莞話唔算係純正廣東話，係簡化版/低音版嘅廣東話/粵語嘅分支，例如無鼻音、某幾個字音/口型無用，如果無練習返特定幾個字，黎到香港講廣東話，會明顯聽得出係東莞人。再細緻啲，每個鎮都有唔同口音嘅東莞話，聽唔慣嘅話，你會唔明隔離鎮啲人講咩。十里一鄉音，以前深圳東莞未改革開放，對外係零交流嘅鄉村，開放咗30年，但上一代照樣用東莞話教育的話好難令下一代人學純正廣東話，傳承問題，所以語言維持不變。改變語言最少要兩代人咁改革先有用，廣州普通話教學，細路開始唔識廣東話，佢地教下一代都教普通話的話，咪統一到語言。你想東莞深圳全部統一廣東話唔係唔得，要一個有系統統一完整嘅20年教育計劃，中共先會做嘅嘢。"},{"pid":"89e3c16b8dc90917d710f58868d2b6ae3bd9335f","tid":510727,"uid":139766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fde36b96c63dd70a0b3e5449f69682c5017efb69","tid":510727,"uid":126590,"like":15,"dislike":54,"score":-39,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"你都忽嘅！<br />\n因爲香港人全部都係由大陸移民落黎囉，唔通靠恥笑人地就真係割裂到個關係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T21:30:11.000Z","msg":"咁都解釋唔到口音嘅問題"},{"pid":"37f585e29d63ae13a3ffa119c1f21de9f1ec7d60","tid":510727,"uid":139766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c513e85784d9bf3bc7fdbed77dae89f0afb2d48a","tid":510727,"uid":115197,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T19:54:33.000Z","msg":"以前得香港北上下一個大城市係廣州<br />\n東莞只係小城 深圳係條村<br />\n啲人係去都去廣州<br />\n所以口音咁近"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T21:33:37.000Z","msg":"有啲道理<br />\n補充咗#3巴打嘅comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d347aafc1e78d52b603801aad6122125